drm/amd/powerplay: refine vce dpm update code on Cz.

Program HardMin based on the vce_arbiter.ecclk
if ecclk is 0, disable ECLK DPM 0. Otherwise VCE
could hang if switching SCLK from DPM 0 to 6/7

